%description
One problem with the biopackages.net RPM approach is porting to MacOS X.
Unlike the Linux distros Fedora and CentOS, the core system packages seem to be
managed with a non-RPM-based system. This means all of the RPM requirements
(build or install time) that are normally provided via the core distro repo are
not available.  Yet many of the core software packages (such as perl and bash)
are actually available.  This package attempts to do two things.  First, create
a fake RPM that "provides" packages for software components already installed
and configured in Mac OS X.  Second, this package will create symbolic links in
the /usr/local directory back to either /sw (for Fink installed packages) or
the Mac OS X native directories.  This will bridge already installed software
with what is required by RPM-based packages.

%prep
%setup -qn %{name}-%{version}

%build

%install

%post

echo 'PATH=/usr/local/bin:/usr/local/sbin:$PATH; PERL5LIB=/usr/local/lib/perl5/site_perl:$PERL5LIB' >> /etc/bashrc
echo 'setenv PATH "/usr/local/bin:/usr/local/sbin:$PATH"; setenv PERL5LIB "/usr/local/lib/perl5/site_perl:$PERL5LIB"' >> /etc/csh.login
echo 'PATH="/usr/local/bin:/usr/local/sbin:$PATH"; PERL5LIB="/usr/local/lib/perl5/site_perl:$PERL5LIB"' >> /etc/profile
rm /Network/Library 
ln -s /Library /Network/Library
ln -s /usr/bin/perl /usr/local/bin/perl
# links for xerces libs
mkdir -p /usr/local/include
ln -s /sw/include/xercesc /usr/local/include/xercesc
ln -s /sw/lib/*xerces* /usr/local/lib/

# now bootstrap the system with fink
fink -y install apache2 apache2-dev apache2-common apache2-mpm-wo apr apr-common apr-shlibs apt apt-shlibs aquaterm aquaterm-dev aquaterm-shlib autoconf2.5 base-files bash bison bzip2 bzip2-dev bzip2-shlibs cctools-extra compress-zlib- daemonic db43-shlibs debianutils dpkg expat expat-shlibs f2c fink fink-mirrors fink-prebindin fontconfig2-sh fort77 freetype219 freetype219-sh g95 gawk gcc4 gcc4-shlibs gd-bin gd-shlibs gd2 gd2-shlibs gdbm-shlibs gdbm3 gdbm3-shlibs gettext gettext-bin gettext-dev gettext-tools glib glib-shlibs gmp gmp-shlibs gzip html-parser-pm html-tagset-pm image-base-pm image-xpm-pm lesstif lesstif-shlibs libgcrypt libgcrypt-shli libgeos2 libgeos2-shlib libgettext3-sh libgmpxx4-shli libgpg-error-s libiconv libiconv-bin libiconv-dev libjpeg libjpeg-bin libjpeg-shlibs libmpfr1 libmpfr1-shlib libncurses5 libncurses5-sh libpng3 libpng3-shlibs libwww-pm586 libxml2 libxml2-bin libxml2-shlibs libxslt libxslt-bin libxslt-shlibs links m4 make mysql mysql-client mysql-dev mysql-shlibs mysql15-shlibs ncurses ncurses-shlibs netcdf netcdf-bin netcdf-shlibs odcctools openssl openssl-dev openssl-shlibs passwd pgplot pkgconfig postgresql80 postgresql80-d postgresql80-s postgresql80-u proj proj-shlibs pth-shlibs readline-shlib readline5 readline5-shli system-openssl tar unzip uri-pm586 wget xerces-c xerces-c-dev xerces-c-shlib xml-parser-pm5

